high_descs: go to the cabinet to the right of the stove
pick up the tea kettle from the cabinet below on the right
take the kettle to the sink
fill the kettle with water from the sink
take the kettle to the bottom cabinet to the left of the sink
put the kettle in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: fill a kettle with water to put in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the sink and walk to the stove.
Pick up the tea kettle to the right of the stove on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the tea kettle inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and hang a right at the stove to face the cabinet under the counter.
Open the large cabinet on the left, put the rinsed tea kettle inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed tea kettle in a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the kettle from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the kettle down inside the sink, rinse off the kettle, pick it up from the sink.
Face the cabinet below the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the cabinet door, put the kettle in the cabinet, close the door.
anns.task_desc: To rinse a kettle and put it in the cabinet.
